{"tid":313642,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老闆比左2個選擇我","createTime":"2017-07-08T13:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T13:30:45.000Z","uid":121730,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8a0db3e79bf333a8c0743cf1c706e623f8be6d","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"今日老闆話可以加我地人工，但要我地簡邊個plan <br />\nPlan A: 炒左一個長工，有雙糧，遲下請一個pt<br />\nPlan B : 可以三個留底但無雙糧 <br />\n其實邊個plan 好小小？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：走個個一定係我，佢地岩岩做呢行無經驗出面好難搵工，我之前有做過呢行，所以經驗比佢地多。出面搵工易過佢地好多。"},{"pid":"e140c3280827e707f39803e56b3a2f3710bc5a21","tid":313642,"uid":342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"遲下請返你做pt<br />\n叫個兩條蛋散分返錢比你"},{"pid":"79494a75a9bd74ddfa6e60bcde50d9e929d4972e","tid":313642,"uid":53238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"點解炒你<br />\n叫其中一個冇經驗轉 pt"},{"pid":"dcf31bcd12f4f21a6af1d2c96a4a09c8611f932a","tid":313642,"uid":48631,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"乜你老闆會諗埋炒邊個會易搵工D咁好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2967ca8288a56117b53d6da0c6500e03aca797","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜你老闆會諗埋炒邊個會易搵工D咁好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無，只係叫我地諗邊個plan, 我自己諗過係我走比較好"},{"pid":"f919bbe37630c3bd2a1b9c84f5d3f8e61703db28","tid":313642,"uid":54754,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"PLAN C: 叫埋個三個一齊炒老闆魷魚"},{"pid":"23aa767384890741fb9421a4976da614488d7c13","tid":313642,"uid":25794,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"三個一齊走佢自己做晒"},{"pid":"9be491697907e92267c2e36ab783d858ef4abd23","tid":313642,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"492516a45d66ba0fc9f4bda7d652f71c1e0c66d7","tid":313642,"uid":82398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"第三條路全部一齊走"},{"pid":"0dc1d8ddf36620f4b771fb80c7e644877c9bed5b","tid":313642,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa2e5390c8d2a60038a7861c644ef1eed90e61a","tid":313642,"uid":9769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"D咁既老闆你仲縱容佢，屌佢老母然後三個一齊走啦"},{"pid":"5e447bf135048db5814a70afb94e2033948e4886","tid":313642,"uid":112747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"plan b其實即係唔加人工?"},{"pid":"960060b7f8e3cd966789998326c2a44b74e2efa4","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>plan b其實即係唔加人工?</blockquote><br />\n有加既，但小左雙糧"},{"pid":"3c9bc51921c6323690973bd691bf1454ec2571c9","tid":313642,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"Plan C: 炒9老闆,自己搵過份更好"},{"pid":"df01a379e40fee7d6725b063d8f995969da9fd27","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加人工但加工作量 咪即係一個人做2份工作量</blockquote><br />\n我地而家因為最低工資實施左，無啦啦cut 鐘 ，所以變成輪班，真係好辛苦，一個人做三個人野，所以同佢講，叫佢還完番以前既模式，佢就比左呢2個plan 我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce873935804edd035ac1d26044051f5a9a1b186","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第三條路全部一齊走</blockquote><br />\n我地有諗過，但留低個pt 係到好慘，佢要照顧家庭先至保住份工，如果又得番佢一個佢會令病情加重<br />\n利申佢之前係呢度番full time ，但番工番到有情緒病而家食緊藥先轉pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d494c52f585746894a6699e84553f743f86382e","tid":313642,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"A 喇當然，個同事layoff之後可能搵得好過依家<br />\n<br />\n你幫左佢"},{"pid":"f0ae7c54d7183cccafe53c03c0cb7cf67f9f675c","tid":313642,"uid":101650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"同另外兩個傾好, 一齊入房屌佢老母辭職<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">然後偷偷地返轉頭食回頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f96eb042b60f7d30866107eec56579f7e944087c","tid":313642,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"三個一齊走。"},{"pid":"78041aa6168c215ccf884c715ba0d80e280da5f6","tid":313642,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"三個一齊走，腦細加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8437edb41c752a51e1cb3350a6580357c11be6","tid":313642,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第三條路全部一齊走</blockquote><br />\n我地有諗過，但留低個pt 係到好慘，佢要照顧家庭先至保住份工，如果又得番佢一個佢會令病情加重<br />\n利申佢之前係呢度番full time ，但番工番到有情緒病而家食緊藥先轉pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩工嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係行頭窄到咁緊要 轉工都唔得?<br />\n有冇必要返工返到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咪離地?"},{"pid":"17a728422ef48fa3860481232910778ab8cb1456","tid":313642,"uid":35199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"連哩d 決定都唔做，學