唔係咁做,冇人會多謝你<br />\n但就算2個細既多謝你咁,唔可以當飯食"},{"pid":"58355b46f65021a4c5b6cdfa4d92a6acebfb0b72","tid":313642,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d83f3cb44b214c9fe9308ac8077384b059d5a9c","tid":313642,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"最低工資咪撚做啦<br />\n3個一齊唔撈飛起你老細"},{"pid":"405a6b8ee59012929c043034eb8485d53893a62c","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜你老闆會諗埋炒邊個會易搵工D咁好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無，只係叫我地諗邊個plan, 我自己諗過係我走比較好</blockquote><br />\n做好人唔係咁做,冇人會多謝你<br />\n但就算2個細既多謝你咁,唔可以當飯食</blockquote><br />\n又唔係話做好人既，咁本身好受氣都想唔做，咁而家突然掉2個plan 出黎，真係唔知點簡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feb7bddfa4e455f008163b53e1f023bb2097a74","tid":313642,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"多左幾多工作量呀 有同無雙糧差唔夠10% 3減1明搵笨<br />\n咁濕鳩不如轉工"},{"pid":"5ef3d5f6b8b129a952031749b16ca822e41cb19c","tid":313642,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜你老闆會諗埋炒邊個會易搵工D咁好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無，只係叫我地諗邊個plan, 我自己諗過係我走比較好</blockquote><br />\n做好人唔係咁做,冇人會多謝你<br />\n但就算2個細既多謝你咁,唔可以當飯食</blockquote><br />\n又唔係話做好人既，咁本身好受氣都想唔做，咁而家突然掉2個plan 出黎，真係唔知點簡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你覺得個老闆閪既唔想做咁咪就囉,但我覺得唔好洗人諗埋後路,唔係害鳩人或者蹺起人咪得囉