:665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"如果你本身已經好有決心想走既 咪當成全其他人 自己走囉"},{"pid":"0b6fbbbac7596b3f214a75b12306d0d2d8d66cfe","tid":313642,"uid":49461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"想知邊行多d"},{"pid":"b9b6e0f4c6ee459c28a460d778997add889d8805","tid":313642,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r0w8mcaf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr0w8mcaf&h=26af2bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n兩子之母珊迪娜患憂鬱症後復工，老闆發現只要同工加班頂替她，工廠仍能運作如常，於是開出一個「民主」方案：十六位員工投票決定讓她留下，抑或把她解雇然後獲一千歐元。珊迪娜為保飯碗，要在兩天一夜內逐戶游說所有同事，面對的卻是各家自有難唸的經。賺到盡的企業計算與為求生計不顧尊嚴的工人困境，現實面前，正義何價"},{"pid":"4a7427a05c4cd6e633b02cf102b2476a93943e3c","tid":313642,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"做邊行咁仆街 最低工資加個少少都cut人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f4ab4cd4f730424be19f99f41e557f037275ba","tid":313642,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做邊行咁仆街 最低工資加個少少都cut人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都奇怪,樓主講到唔似冇技術含量既工,但係又最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b72bdf748cd1603d65d47e0755a10882a807d9c","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做邊行咁仆街 最低工資加個少少都cut人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都奇怪,樓主講到唔似冇技術含量既工,但係又最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a78ef2c7b658451999e613b159c9905c9ce957","tid":313642,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做邊行咁仆街 最低工資加個少少都cut人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都奇怪,樓主講到唔似冇技術含量既工,但係又最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認所姑娘?認真估唔到你地係收最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3541297b3cf16292966938468894bcda3df81f12","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做邊行咁仆街 最低工資加個少少都cut人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都奇怪,樓主講到唔似冇技術含量既工,但係又最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認所姑娘?認真估唔到你地係收最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，係低到唔低個種，由番工到收工都受緊d 病人氣 ，執藥慢小小又駡，登記慢小小又駡。佢唔到收工個一秒都唔黎睇病，叫佢下午個段時間先黎又話病到就黎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講快小小又話態度差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e3fa6039e89177286ed66e0b661a1fddbe8984","tid":313642,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"所以話最低工資同強積金根本冇so<br />\n<br />\n班低下層仲以為執到寶，抵佢地窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25155fea41e76f81cd4a464bcd73f4316595ccda","tid":313642,"uid":70368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"你老細出多一份糧都出唔起<br />\nquit啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a62ca5f740980a7f5fbe2ce7486b0c2e8b9688d","tid":313642,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"怪唔得話診所醫生月入過十皮 原來姑娘最低工資出糧 每日有無8個鐘？仲要一星期五日 咪一皮都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca266879677904964f94d775b95526f1d233b1aa","tid":313642,"uid":121730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怪唔得話診所醫生月入過十皮 原來姑娘最低工資出糧 每日有無8個鐘？仲要一星期五日 咪一皮都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢間診所開9.5小時，本身我地番9.5 小時 ，最低工資後cut 左我地番8.5 ，變相我地要自己單獨應付一個鐘，既要出藥又要登記又要幫佢地開門，先再叫病人入去見醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多人起上黎唔好話講野快，唔黑你面巳經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}